Reviews.original: The artwork effectively uses contrasting colors to enhance visual interest. The red mat stands out vividly against the black and gray background, drawing attention to the dog. The black walls provide a stark contrast to the lighter colors of the dog, making the subject more prominent. However, the contrast could be more pronounced in some areas to create an even more striking visual impact.
